    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏由《X-COM 幽浮》创始人 Julian Gollop 打造，结合了第三人称动作与即时战略的独特玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >外星脑怪入侵了地球，并用重力球盗走了珍贵的脑晶。只有年轻的发明家和他的机器猫——奇普和爪兹能够阻止脑怪的邪恶计划，夺回每个重力球，并一路攻上母舰！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332430/extras/c75970f9f2204bac30f7adb07f09ad94.poster.avif?t=1760381668\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332430/extras/c75970f9f2204bac30f7adb07f09ad94.webm?t=1760381668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332430/extras/c75970f9f2204bac30f7adb07f09ad94.mp4?t=1760381668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动作与策略的融合</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在单人或合作模式中化身英勇的奇普和爪兹，在幽默风趣的故事战役和多样的支线任务中阻止脑怪的侵袭。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快节奏的任务让你随时都能投入战斗，简单易学但深度十足的游戏机制为经典策略游戏带来了现代化的诠释。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在对抗脑怪的战斗中，建造基地、武器、载具和能力库，带领你的军队冲锋陷阵！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过战略指挥视角组建并指挥你的军队，并在大规模战斗中与他们并肩作战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最强大的脑怪首领展开 Boss 战，这将对你的基地管理和战斗指挥能力提出终极考验！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332430/extras/3027f45981e2ff9d08dc3c2e6fa56997.poster.avif?t=1760381668\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332430/extras/3027f45981e2ff9d08dc3c2e6fa56997.webm?t=1760381668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332430/extras/3027f45981e2ff9d08dc3c2e6fa56997.mp4?t=1760381668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种多人游戏模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友并肩作战或一较高下，在史诗级多人战役中尽情厮杀！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双人本地同屏作战，双倍乐趣——与好友协同战术，一起击败脑怪军团！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投身 PvP 混战——经典的线上 1v1、2v2 模式，与朋友组队或在分屏 1v1 中一决高下！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跨平台联机支持，在 PC 和主机上邀请任何人加入你的冒险战役或 PvP 对战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332430/extras/08b629cadb9b5159e1bfb7d2ae19ed60.poster.avif?t=1760381668\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332430/extras/08b629cadb9b5159e1bfb7d2ae19ed60.webm?t=1760381668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332430/extras/08b629cadb9b5159e1bfb7d2ae19ed60.mp4?t=1760381668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >漫画风格与叙事</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏设定在一个明亮而充满活力的宇宙中，将玩家带入一个全新的、复古漫画风格的世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险的过程中遇到一群令人难忘的角色，脑怪军团的奇葩角色轮番登场，每个“瓶装脑怪”都有自己的小故事！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索关卡的每个角落，收集稀有道具，解锁秘密剧情，如揭开脑怪入侵之谜的漫画书，建造新武器、升级小兵和英雄能力的设计图。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
